{"about_the_game":"Players will embark on a first-person experience in ArroGation: Unlight Of Day that is full of suspense, thrills, anD the unknown. You wiLl dElve into the abandoned village of Yunlin and confront the Specter that hideS in the darkness.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/x09.gif?t=1677158174\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/te1.png?t=1677158174\" /><br><br>In this village shrouded in the darkness lurks a multitude of monsters you have never seen before, and their tragic experiences and resentments seem to be hidden beneath their frightening appearance.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/x07.gif?t=1677158174\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/x01.gif?t=1677158174\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/te2.png?t=1677158174\" /><br><br>The history of Yunlin Village has too many secrets to be explored - those strange customs, mysterious rituals, and unexplained riddles. All revealing a looming crisis!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/x02.gif?t=1677158174\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/x05.gif?t=1677158174\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/te3.png?t=1677158174\" /><br><br>Being in a gloomy and crisis-filled village, you must use all possible means to escape from here. Explore carefully in order to escape.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/x08.gif?t=1677158174\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/x03.gif?t=1677158174\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/te4.png?t=1677158174\" /><br><br>Various styles of puzzles are all over the map, sounds, light, garbage, and even scary monsters can be key clues. The puzzle may be hidden in the most unexpected places.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/x10.gif?t=1677158174\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/x04.gif?t=1677158174\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/te5.png?t=1677158174\" /><br><br>From the ancient miracles, to the atrocities of the Imperial Japanese army in World War II, and then to the unpredictable cult. Why did this originally peaceful village fall into the darkness without light? The answer to everything lies in this horrific flame!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113530/extras/x06.gif?t=1677158174\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Going Home","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2113530/c42247c82f790bd1807fc6c8b6d2a99a7f5df917.jpg"},{"name":"Inkling Rising","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2113530/0ab6ca8b98be7b77a7e8c67c502dfb323394f3ab.jpg"},{"name":"Travelling Alone","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2113530/2c388293d27a0fb5d134622319ca1a13d544780a.jpg"},{"name":"Life behind Death","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2113530/a50515ec597dc57f